    <briefdescription>
<para>Description of the overlap in 3D space of adjacent tiles. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><ref refid="structTTL__overlap" kindref="compound">TTL_overlap</ref> represents the number of overlapped elements between adjacent tiles in each dimension.</para>
<para>For example, overlap.x=1 means that every horizontally-adjacent tiles share elements on one column.</para>
<para>The type used to hold the overlap between adjacent tiles along all dimensions </para>
    </detaileddescription>
